             <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;Color:rgb(0,0,0);">- Isopachenplan Deckstauer. </span>
            </p>
            <p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">
             <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;Color:rgb(0,0,0);">Übergabe in digitaler Form </span>
             <br/>
             <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;Color:rgb(0,0,0);">- Gesamtunterlage im PDF-Format, </span>
             <br/>
             <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;Color:rgb(0,0,0);">- Lage- und Isopachenpläne im CAD-Zeichnungsformat </span>
            </p>
